{"tid":28770,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"盧寵茂接任港大深圳醫院院長","createTime":"2016-12-08T07:00:49.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-08T18:39:53.000Z","uid":1567,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1df95df0a76b79b6258ba4fead4cd9c5980e6b84","tid":28770,"uid":1567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T07:00:49.000Z","msg":"盧寵茂接任港大深圳醫院院長"},{"pid":"68f24e72bb36d871525e43c8e4270cb2c898679b","tid":28770,"uid":1567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T07:02:20.000Z","msg":"&quot;11月13日下午，香港大學深圳醫院舉行第二任任院長任職儀式，宣布香港大學盧寵茂教正式就任新一任院長。深圳市副市長，港大深圳醫院董事長吳以環為盧寵茂教授頒發院長聘書。深圳市公立醫院管理中心主任王大平，黨組書記張丹;香港大學李嘉誠醫學院院長梁卓偉等嘉賓出席當天儀式。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今年10月20日，經香港大學深圳醫院第一屆董事會第九次會議研究決定：盧寵茂教授任香港大學深圳醫院院長，聘期於2016年11月14日起，為期五年。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hku-szh.org/KindEditor/attached/image/20161114/20161114171848_4576.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hku-szh.org%2FKindEditor%2Fattached%2Fimage%2F20161114%2F20161114171848_4576.jpg&h=b7b460cd&s={SIZE}\" />&quot;<br />\n<br />\n盧寵茂教授履新院長一職（2016年11月14日）。香港大學深圳醫院。<a href=\"http://www.hku-szh.org/NewsInfo3176.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hku-szh.org%2FNewsInfo3176.html&d=K5fC9J%2FDBXU5QSe0Qq%2F4kksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=6c3a2cb4\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hku-szh.org/NewsInfo3176.html</a>"},{"pid":"1243221dc8a3171a3be4b5b259a6f6fc6ae9b1f5","tid":28770,"uid":498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:23:52.000Z","msg":"算唔算流放鬼國"},{"pid":"9ce36a303d563dfb672391bab5bcec6c6a4eb3c7","tid":28770,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:25:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6b1fd0bf510d0bb5a79636a159a824ab8610cce6","tid":28770,"uid":8171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:26:10.000Z","msg":"淪為行過寵謬"},{"pid":"530a7ed4d69dcbda33959ec76e06f85f90c530ef","tid":28770,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T10:03:40.000Z","msg":"舔共狗"},{"pid":"914c3843db1a4bc2d7b520c7e345603f841dd1b7","tid":28770,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T10:51:17.000Z","msg":"之前港大單嘢既政治交易"},{"pid":"0375b86cf91ddb370c543cae86f894ac365b0420","tid":28770,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T13:02:00.000Z","msg":"非法人體器官移植中心院長。"},{"pid":"de5a9606365d6985db9aeea32acabc5b205ec155","tid":28770,"uid":42435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T15:55:08.000Z","msg":"好快比支那病人家屬打鑊金下跪認錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b259b289c65c04b3884a86732bf070b09f7abe82","tid":28770,"uid":42435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T15:56:22.000Z","msg":"反獨有功，返支那合法收紅包<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b08e6ab43592cea92f544f8ea75308ffa2a25198","tid":28770,"uid":33653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T18:39:53.000Z","msg":"插水院長"}]}